      "estimated_duration_s": 9.0,
      "narration_text": "In 1993, IBM physicists arranged 48 iron atoms in a ring on a copper surface. Inside the ring, the STM image showed concentric ripples \u2014 rings of electron density nobody put there. Quantum mechanics put them there.",
