      "t_start": 38.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10.0,
      "narration_text": "The surviving modes are discrete. The first mode has one central peak \u2014 the ground state. The second mode has a central peak and one ring. Each mode has a fixed number of radial nodes, and those nodes show up as dark rings in the STM image.",
