      "beat_id": "B07",
      "t_start": 58.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10.0,
      "narration_text": "The key point: the experimenters did not put these rings there. They placed 48 iron atoms in a circle and walked away. The quantum boundary condition produced the rings automatically \u2014 the same way a guitar string produces specific harmonics because its ends are fixed.",
