    {
      "beat_id": "B08",
      "t_start": 68.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10.0,
      "narration_text": "The quantum corral is not a special phenomenon. It is just quantization made visible. Every quantum dot, every semiconductor well, every atom \u2014 they all have discrete states because their boundary conditions forbid everything else. The corral made this literal: you can see it.",
